Hello, Customer!

Thanks for your order. Here is the total and each item in your order.

===============================================


<% @order.line_items.each do |line_item| %>
      <% if product = Product.find_by(id: line_item.product_id) %>

           >Item: <%= product.name %>

           Quantity: <%= line_item.quantity %>

           Total: <%= line_item.item_price_cents * line_item.quantity / 100.0 %>


      <% end %>
    <% end %>
